data.description: Desirable craftsman-style 2 story home in Riverbend! Updated with new carpet and tasteful interior paint, this home is move-in ready. Gas logs in Great Room with lots of windows and light! Landscaped backyard with paver patio and fence backs up to common area. Garage has double doors and a full rubber mat on floor. Hardwoods on main gleam. White on white kitchen earns style points. Two walk-in closets in master suite, plus double vanities and separate shower and garden tub in master bath.
